Package es.uvigo.esei.amchartsjava.core.validators

This package contains validators to paths, idiom and values of properties,also cast to concrete chart,graph,guide,trendLine or Axis

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AxisValidator
    This class contains methods to cast Axis to concrete axis.
    ChartValidator
    This class contains methods to cast AmChartController to concrete chart.
    ColorValidator
    This class contains validators to format of color.
    GraphValidator
    This class contains methods to cast graphs to concrete graph.
    GuideValidator
    This class contains methods to cast guides to concrete guide.
    IdiomValidator
    This class contains validator to chose idiom.
    NumberValidator
    This class contains validators to numbers.
    PathValidator
    This class contains validators to path.
    PropertyValidator
    This class contains string and pattern validators.
    TrendLineValidator
    This class contains methods to cast TrendLines to concrete trendLine.
